connectAccountPage.subtitleString: Keep personal and business orders separate with effortless switching between accounts

accountActions.actionSubtitleString: Create a separate personal account that uses a different email and connect it.
Connect an existing personal account that uses a different email.

convertAccountPage.subtitleString: Simplify your experience and return to personal use, with adjustments to how your account works.

valueProps.subtitleString: Your order history, addresses, and payment methods will appear in your business account.
You can add up to 5 family members to your account
You'll be able to use EBT SNAP with your personal account.

inaccessibleValueProps.titleString: Benefits you can't access with your personal account

valueProps.subtitleString: Your team members will no longer have access to this business account
You can no longer bulk export receipts.

warningBanner.messageString: You're about to convert your business account to a personal account. You can switch back to a business account at any time.

learnMorePage.titleString: Shop for your business with an Instacart Business account

valueProps.subtitleString: Enjoy the benefits of Instacart, plus special business features and tools.
Your order history, addresses, and payment methods will appear in your business account.
Give others permission to place orders, view analytics, or manage permissions.
Bulk export order receipts for easy expense management.
Order from your favorite local stores, retailers, and distributors.
Eligible businesses can save on eligible tax-exempt items.

signup.altTitleString: Sign up for a personal account

login.altTitleString: Log in to your personal account
